razorqt (0.5.2+20130326-1nano) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream git 0.5.2+20130326
  * debian/control:
    + remove VCS-entries
    + minor indention changes
    + make razorqt depend on udisks, so that automounting
      devices properly works (does not work with udisks2)
  * upstream:
    + fixed appearance icons display + huge filesystem
      access optimization in this area
    + Proper scaling of razor-lightdm-greeter background
    + Fix Issue #564 (new panel: cfg "Line size" can be
      set to 10px but the value is not accepted)
    + Fix Issue #563 ( #563 "new panel: vertical mode
      makes panel too large (width)")
    + New functions
      RazorGridLayout::setCellMinimumHeight
      RazorGridLayout::setCellMinimumWidth
      RazorGridLayout::setCellMaximumWidth
      RazorGridLayout::setCellMaximumHeight
      RazorGridLayout::setCellFixedSize
      RazorGridLayout::setCellFixedHeight
      RazorGridLayout::setCellFixedWidth
    + razor-lightdm-greeter: configurable background and
      loginform positioning
    + razor-lightdm-greeter: Standardize loading of stylesheets
    + optimized panel calculations for icons only mode

